  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Chef de Nouvelles",
      "effect": "If this card on the field is Tributed and added to the Extra Deck face-up: You can place this card in your Pendulum Zone. You cannot activate the following effects of \"Chef de Nouvelles\" in the same Chain. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 Effect Monster on the field; increase its Level by up to 3. Once per turn, if your opponent Special Summons a monster(s) (except during the Damage Step): You can banish 1 \"Recipe\" Ritual Spell from your hand, Deck, or GY; apply that card's activation effect that Ritual Summons a monster.",
      "pendulumEffect": "During your Main Phase, if this card was activated this turn: You can add 1 \"Nouvelles\" card from your Deck to your hand, except a Pendulum Monster. If a monster(s) is Special Summoned to your opponent's field (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card. You can only use each effect of \"Chef de Nouvelles\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
